{
  "stem": "21319.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were 20, 30 people, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At a big table-- table that was as long as this room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And he said to me, shh.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My child, don't ever complain and say a thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Be grateful, she said, that you can give and help.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the last several years, at times, were very bad because of anti-Semitism and boycotting the Jewish stores, and the Jewish business.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- my mother had-- we struggled very hard to survive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was like, 1935, something, from-- till-- because when that Jozef Pilsudski was the President.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he-- he was a very good man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I think his wife was Jewish or something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He treated the Jews equally.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when he died, the anti-Semitism in full flare.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Germany, naturally, was under the Nazis already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And with tremendous influence.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And going [INAUDIBLE] my parents struggled very hard to survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was very hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For us?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It started in 1939, when the bombs were falling over our head.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were bombing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and then Hitler made a pact with Stalin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Stalin kept-- Vilna was a part of Lithuania because Vilna-- the-- the Russians took.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the other part, Hitler took.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So Warsaw was under Hitler.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we had no-- no deals with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have-- I can't-- there-- That was such a short time that I really have no memories.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came in 1940.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some times, I don't know which month.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And six months later, I think, the Nazis came in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was only six months, they were there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I know when the Nazis came in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was June 21, 1941.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to get papers, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
